{"tid":2103584,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"究竟口罩係咪真係咁有用？","createTime":"2020-07-11T10:06:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T02:52:51.000Z","uid":222614,"like":5,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"2ac73460d87aeea77b37aab69f90aae3c2769ada","tid":2103584,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T10:06:13.000Z","msg":"香港人以自律為榮，聲稱戴口罩係為左保護他人，又將香港疫情緩和歸功於自己，並鄙視美加反對強制戴口罩措施嘅民眾<br />\n<br />\n對香港人黎講，口罩如光環，詳見：<br />\n<br />\n知唔知係美加就黎有場杖要打？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2094624\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2094624</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n最近爆發第三波令口罩價格再次暴漲，香港人為左保護他人，亦不惜捱炒價大量入貨<br />\n<br />\n如果疫情緩和要歸功於口罩，咁再次爆發又應該歸咎於誰？<br />\n<br />\n究竟口罩係咪真係咁有用？"},{"pid":"511126affdc11a0759b67eb5f1e4251d1d050278","tid":2103584,"uid":91017,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T10:12:53.000Z","msg":"跨境學童<br />\n餐廳門口求鳩其射測温槍<br />\n港泰員工"},{"pid":"87d6222f7bcfea9bdbd987b7893df4378dcc8097","tid":2103584,"uid":27553,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T10:15:15.000Z","msg":"一早應該信國師用銀離子超長效洗手凝膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"361577627786cb81add9596553a88af5be65dc6d","tid":2103584,"uid":197761,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T10:20:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"793e2842821ccb6cb913aeae92ed168fb6ccf242","tid":2103584,"uid":353482,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T10:23:31.000Z","msg":"防疫呢d要多管齊下做"},{"pid":"0e53eadea56f60bd90ad8e498f2b8f25a012c459","tid":2103584,"uid":301100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T10:35:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />袁國勇咪出過論文表明口罩有效囉屌"},{"pid":"8b93964b9e7edbf92824c2b6eab0f1a36a46bfc7","tid":2103584,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"0e53eadea56f60bd90ad8e498f2